### **2. `.chezmoiignore`**
```
# Ignore Docker binaries and generated files
{{ if ne .chezmoi.os "darwin" }}
.config/ghostty/
{{ end }}

# Ignore based on profile
{{ if ne .profile "devops" }}
.config/zsh/plugins/kubectl.plugin.zsh
.config/zsh/plugins/terraform.plugin.zsh
{{ end }}

{{ if ne .profile "backend" }}
.config/zsh/plugins/docker.plugin.zsh
{{ end }}

# Always ignore
.config/docker/bin/
.config/docker/.docker/bin/
.config/docker/contexts/
.config/docker/private_*/
.config/docker/models/
.config/docker/mcp/
.config/tmux/plugins/*/.git/
